===Etymology===
Perhaps an areal word; compare {{cog|th|เอว|t=waist}} ({{zh-ref|Schuessler, 2007}}), if not borrowed from the Chinese. Schuessler's additional comparison of a {{ncog|hmn-pro||*qlauᴮ|t=waist, lower back}} (whence {{ncog|mww|duav|t=waist}}), appears phonetically suspect due to the proto-form being more commonly reconstructed as {{m|hmn-pro||*qlajX}}. Note also similarities to {{cog|my|အူ|t=intestines}} ({{zh-ref|Luce, 1981}}).

